metadata.dc:description: Report of one tracheocele case casually uncovered in a man 51-year-old. Starting from the difference between congenital and acquired cases of this pathology the AA. refer to the symptomatologic picture, to diagnostical and therapeutical measures as well, pinpointing to possible complications that may arise specially by infants during the lactation period.
metadata.dc:title: Traqueocele Presentación de un caso.
[Tracheocele: a case report].
